{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":460,"text":"Clouds."},{"time":2770,"text":"Have you ever noticed how much\npeople moan about them?"},{"time":5392,"text":"They get a bad rap."},{"time":7639,"text":"If you think about it,\nthe English language"},{"time":10186,"text":"has written into it negative\nassociations towards the clouds."},{"time":14479,"text":"Someone who's down or depressed,"},{"time":16946,"text":"they're under a cloud."},{"time":18637,"text":"And when there's bad news in store,"},{"time":20328,"text":"there's a cloud on the horizon."},{"time":23176,"text":"I saw an article the other day."},{"time":25208,"text":"It was about problems\nwith computer processing"},{"time":28394,"text":"over the Internet."},{"time":30216,"text":"\"A cloud over the cloud,\"\nwas the headline."},{"time":35140,"text":"It seems like they're everyone's default"},{"time":37123,"text":"doom-and-gloom metaphor."},{"time":39397,"text":"But I think they're beautiful, don't you?"},{"time":41550,"text":"It's just that their beauty is missed"},{"time":44663,"text":"because they're so omnipresent,"},{"time":46663,"text":"so, I don't know, commonplace,"},{"time":50012,"text":"that people don't notice them."},{"time":51465,"text":"They don't notice the beauty,\nbut they don't even notice the clouds"},{"time":54680,"text":"unless they get in the way of the sun."},{"time":56957,"text":"And so people think of clouds as"},{"time":59262,"text":"things that get in the way."},{"time":61342,"text":"They think of them as the annoying,\nfrustrating obstructions,"},{"time":66413,"text":"and then they rush off and do\nsome blue-sky thinking."},{"time":69333,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":71718,"text":"But most people, when\nyou stop to ask them,"},{"time":73941,"text":"will admit to harboring a strange\nsort of fondness for clouds."},{"time":78791,"text":"It's like a nostalgic fondness,"},{"time":81450,"text":"and they make them think of their youth."},{"time":84584,"text":"Who here can't remember thinking, well,"},{"time":87820,"text":"looking and finding shapes in the clouds"},{"time":90422,"text":"when they were kids?"},{"time":91765,"text":"You know, when you were\nmasters of daydreaming?"},{"time":98496,"text":"Aristophanes, the ancient\nGreek playwright,"},{"time":101263,"text":"he described the clouds\nas the patron godesses"},{"time":104614,"text":"of idle fellows"},{"time":106398,"text":"two and a half thousand years ago,"},{"time":108042,"text":"and you can see what he means."},{"time":109495,"text":"It's just that these days,\nus adults seem reluctant"},{"time":113952,"text":"to allow ourselves the indulgence"},{"time":117312,"text":"of just allowing our imaginations"},{"time":119944,"text":"to drift along in the breeze,\nand I think that's a pity."},{"time":123614,"text":"I think we should perhaps\ndo a bit more of it."},{"time":126000,"text":"I think we should be a bit\nmore willing, perhaps,"},{"time":129020,"text":"to look at the beautiful sight\nof the sunlight bursting out"},{"time":132963,"text":"from behind the clouds\nand go, \"Wait a minute,"},{"time":136429,"text":"that's two cats dancing the salsa!\""},{"time":138768,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":140165,"text":"Or seeing the big, white,\npuffy one up there"},{"time":145931,"text":"over the shopping center looks like"},{"time":147853,"text":"the Abominable Snowman\ngoing to rob a bank."},{"time":151486,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":154682,"text":"They're like nature's version\nof those inkblot images,"},{"time":158600,"text":"you know, that shrinks used\nto show their patients"},{"time":161005,"text":"in the '60s,"},{"time":162272,"text":"and I think if you consider\nthe shapes you see in the clouds,"},{"time":165997,"text":"you'll save money on psychoanalysis bills."},{"time":169887,"text":"Let's say you're in love. All right?"},{"time":171766,"text":"And you look up and what do you see?"},{"time":173963,"text":"Right? Or maybe the opposite."},{"time":176589,"text":"You've just been dumped by your partner,"},{"time":178633,"text":"and everywhere you look,\nit's kissing couples."},{"time":181742,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":183694,"text":"Perhaps you're having a moment\nof existential angst."},{"time":187450,"text":"You know, you're thinking\nabout your own mortality."},{"time":189903,"text":"And there, on the horizon,\nit's the Grim Reaper."},{"time":192899,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":195858,"text":"Or maybe you see a topless sunbather."},{"time":199303,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":200932,"text":"What would that mean?"},{"time":204004,"text":"What would that mean? I have no idea."},{"time":209535,"text":"But one thing I do know is this:"},{"time":211765,"text":"The bad press that clouds\nget is totally unfair."},{"time":215140,"text":"I think we should stand up for them,"},{"time":216879,"text":"which is why, a few years ago,"},{"time":218332,"text":"I started the Cloud Appreciation Society."},{"time":221018,"text":"Tens of thousands of members now"},{"time":223590,"text":"in almost 100 countries around the world."},{"time":225616,"text":"And all these photographs\nthat I'm showing,"},{"time":228617,"text":"they were sent in by members."},{"time":230973,"text":"And the society exists\nto remind people of this:"},{"time":234437,"text":"Clouds are not something to moan about."},{"time":237484,"text":"Far from it. They are, in fact,"},{"time":239867,"text":"the most diverse, evocative,\npoetic aspect of nature."},{"time":247577,"text":"I think, if you live\nwith your head in the clouds"},{"time":250844,"text":"every now and then, it helps you\nkeep your feet on the ground."},{"time":253821,"text":"And I want to show you\nwhy, with the help of"},{"time":255443,"text":"some of my favorite types of clouds."},{"time":257523,"text":"Let's start with this one.\nIt's the cirrus cloud,"},{"time":259880,"text":"named after the Latin for a lock of hair."},{"time":262800,"text":"It's composed entirely of ice crystals"},{"time":264421,"text":"cascading from the upper\nreaches of the troposphere,"},{"time":266937,"text":"and as these ice crystals fall,"},{"time":268438,"text":"they pass through different\nlayers with different winds"},{"time":271082,"text":"and they speed up and slow down,"},{"time":272766,"text":"giving the cloud these\nbrush-stroked appearances,"},{"time":275825,"text":"these brush-stroke forms\nknown as fall streaks."},{"time":278760,"text":"And these winds up there\ncan be very, very fierce."},{"time":280771,"text":"They can be 200 miles\nan hour, 300 miles an hour."},{"time":283352,"text":"These clouds are bombing along,"},{"time":284853,"text":"but from all the way down here,"},{"time":286636,"text":"they appear to be moving\ngracefully, slowly,"},{"time":289784,"text":"like most clouds."},{"time":291993,"text":"And so to tune into the clouds\nis to slow down,"},{"time":295216,"text":"to calm down."},{"time":297161,"text":"It's like a bit of everyday meditation."},{"time":299994,"text":"Those are common clouds."},{"time":301154,"text":"What about rarer ones,\nlike the lenticularis,"},{"time":303956,"text":"the UFO-shaped lenticularis cloud?"},{"time":306307,"text":"These clouds form\nin the region of mountains."},{"time":308827,"text":"When the wind passes, rises\nto pass over the mountain,"},{"time":311712,"text":"it can take on a wave-like\npath in the lee of the peak,"},{"time":314951,"text":"with these clouds hovering at the crest"},{"time":317678,"text":"of these invisible standing waves of air,"},{"time":320338,"text":"these flying saucer-like forms,"},{"time":322600,"text":"and some of the early\nblack-and-white UFO photos"},{"time":325264,"text":"are in fact lenticularis clouds.\nIt's true."},{"time":328180,"text":"A little rarer are the fallstreak holes.\nAll right?"},{"time":332019,"text":"This is when a layer is made\nup of very, very cold"},{"time":334424,"text":"water droplets, and in one region\nthey start to freeze,"},{"time":337271,"text":"and this freezing sets off a chain\nreaction which spreads outwards"},{"time":340438,"text":"with the ice crystals cascading\nand falling down below,"},{"time":343142,"text":"giving the appearance\nof jellyfish tendrils down below."},{"time":347981,"text":"Rarer still, the Kelvinâ€“Helmholtz cloud."},{"time":352061,"text":"Not a very snappy name. Needs a rebrand."},{"time":355503,"text":"This looks like a series\nof breaking waves,"},{"time":359263,"text":"and it's caused by shearing\nwinds -- the wind"},{"time":361957,"text":"above the cloud layer\nand below the cloud layer"},{"time":364220,"text":"differ significantly,\nand in the middle, in between,"},{"time":366775,"text":"you get this undulating of the air,"},{"time":368658,"text":"and if the difference in those\nspeeds is just right,"},{"time":371159,"text":"the tops of the undulations curl over"},{"time":373061,"text":"in these beautiful breaking\nwave-like vortices."},{"time":376623,"text":"All right. Those are rarer\nclouds than the cirrus,"},{"time":379028,"text":"but they're not that rare."},{"time":380735,"text":"If you look up, and you\npay attention to the sky,"},{"time":383583,"text":"you'll see them sooner or later,"},{"time":385456,"text":"maybe not quite as dramatic\nas these, but you'll see them."},{"time":388242,"text":"And you'll see them around where you live."},{"time":390296,"text":"Clouds are the most egalitarian"},{"time":392857,"text":"of nature's displays,\nbecause we all have a good,"},{"time":395531,"text":"fantastic view of the sky."},{"time":398162,"text":"And these clouds, these rarer clouds,"},{"time":400002,"text":"remind us that the exotic can\nbe found in the everyday."},{"time":404722,"text":"Nothing is more nourishing,\nmore stimulating"},{"time":407481,"text":"to an active, inquiring\nmind than being surprised,"},{"time":410948,"text":"being amazed. It's why we're\nall here at TED, right?"},{"time":414644,"text":"But you don't need to rush off"},{"time":417589,"text":"away from the familiar, across the world"},{"time":419949,"text":"to be surprised."},{"time":421411,"text":"You just need to step outside,"},{"time":424186,"text":"pay attention to what's so\ncommonplace, so everyday,"},{"time":426762,"text":"so mundane that everybody else misses it."},{"time":430749,"text":"One cloud that people\nrarely miss is this one:"},{"time":433163,"text":"the cumulonimbus storm cloud."},{"time":436131,"text":"It's what's produces thunder\nand lightning and hail."},{"time":438632,"text":"These clouds spread\nout at the top in this enormous"},{"time":441740,"text":"anvil fashion stretching 10\nmiles up into the atmosphere."},{"time":444562,"text":"They are an expression\nof the majestic architecture"},{"time":447981,"text":"of our atmosphere."},{"time":449866,"text":"But from down below,\nthey are the embodiment"},{"time":453252,"text":"of the powerful, elemental force and power"},{"time":457383,"text":"that drives our atmosphere."},{"time":459277,"text":"To be there is to be connected\nin the driving rain"},{"time":463391,"text":"and the hail, to feel\nconnected to our atmosphere."},{"time":466693,"text":"It's to be reminded that we are creatures"},{"time":468991,"text":"that inhabit this ocean of air."},{"time":470700,"text":"We don't live beneath the sky.\nWe live within it."},{"time":474097,"text":"And that connection, that visceral\nconnection to our atmosphere"},{"time":478180,"text":"feels to me like an antidote."},{"time":480616,"text":"It's an antidote to the growing\ntendency we have"},{"time":483720,"text":"to feel that we can really\never experience life"},{"time":487595,"text":"by watching it on a computer\nscreen, you know,"},{"time":489810,"text":"when we're in a wi-fi zone."},{"time":492260,"text":"But the one cloud that best expresses"},{"time":494544,"text":"why cloudspotting is more\nvaluable today than ever"},{"time":497469,"text":"is this one, the cumulus cloud."},{"time":500660,"text":"Right? It forms on a sunny day."},{"time":502739,"text":"If you close your eyes\nand think of a cloud,"},{"time":504859,"text":"it's probably one of these\nthat comes to mind."},{"time":507208,"text":"All those cloud shapes at the beginning,"},{"time":509832,"text":"those were cumulus clouds."},{"time":511975,"text":"The sharp, crisp outlines\nof this formation"},{"time":515599,"text":"make it the best\none for finding shapes in."},{"time":518755,"text":"And it reminds us"},{"time":520727,"text":"of the aimless nature of cloudspotting,"},{"time":524671,"text":"what an aimless activity it is."},{"time":526920,"text":"You're not going to change the world"},{"time":528659,"text":"by lying on your back and gazing\nup at the sky, are you?"},{"time":532711,"text":"It's pointless. It's a pointless activity,"},{"time":534934,"text":"which is precisely why it's so important."},{"time":539790,"text":"The digital world\nconspires to make us feel"},{"time":543819,"text":"eternally busy, perpetually busy."},{"time":546590,"text":"You know, when you're not dealing with"},{"time":548424,"text":"the traditional pressures\nof earning a living"},{"time":551102,"text":"and putting food on the table,\nraising a family,"},{"time":553756,"text":"writing thank you letters,"},{"time":555830,"text":"you have to now contend with"},{"time":558542,"text":"answering a mountain of unanswered emails,"},{"time":562108,"text":"updating a Facebook page,"},{"time":563966,"text":"feeding your Twitter feed."},{"time":566514,"text":"And cloudspotting\nlegitimizes doing nothing."},{"time":570300,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":572205,"text":"And sometimes we need â€”"},{"time":574857,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":580465,"text":"Sometimes we need excuses to do nothing."},{"time":584548,"text":"We need to be reminded by these"},{"time":587330,"text":"patron goddesses of idle fellows"},{"time":590862,"text":"that slowing down"},{"time":593837,"text":"and being in the present,\nnot thinking about"},{"time":597640,"text":"what you've got to do\nand what you should have done,"},{"time":600494,"text":"but just being here,\nletting your imagination"},{"time":603229,"text":"lift from the everyday concerns down here"},{"time":605991,"text":"and just being in the present,\nit's good for you,"},{"time":608823,"text":"and it's good for the way you feel."},{"time":610961,"text":"It's good for your ideas.\nIt's good for your creativity."},{"time":614529,"text":"It's good for your soul."},{"time":617879,"text":"So keep looking up,"},{"time":620106,"text":"marvel at the ephemeral beauty,"},{"time":623159,"text":"and always remember to live life\nwith your head in the clouds."},{"time":626583,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":627770,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}